{"tid":2433510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共發函「恢復政治權利」 中國網友傻眼：今年最大冷笑話","createTime":"2021-03-05T02:58:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T10:06:50.000Z","uid":337052,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"42c0086863e03cc7ce5be5e8b83dfa61b34d6b92","tid":2433510,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T02:58:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">中共發函「恢復政治權利」 中國網友傻眼：今年最大冷笑話</span></strong><br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/03/05/phpnB6yn5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F03%2F05%2FphpnB6yn5.jpg&h=26f73d8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國民主黨創始人之一朱虞夫屢遭中共當局迫害，頻頻遭監控、拘禁，近日他收到一紙「恢復政治權利通知書」，卻讓不少中國網友全傻眼。（美聯社、推特，本報合成）<br />\n<br />\n2021/03/05 10:40<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕<span class=\"red\">中國民主黨創始人之一朱虞夫屢遭中共當局迫害，頻頻遭監控、拘禁，近日他收到一紙「恢復政治權利通知書」，卻讓不少中國網友全傻眼，直呼「中國一出生就被剝奪政治權利了」、「我們有政治權利嗎？」</span><br />\n<br />\n中國異議人士朱虞夫是中國民主黨創始人之一，多次遭受當局打壓、刑拘，屢次被以「顛覆國家政權」定罪。2011年他被判有期徒刑7年，並於2018年3月獲釋，但獲釋後仍被當局嚴密監控。<br />\n<br />\n中國人權律師劉曉原3日在推特上貼出杭州市公安局發給朱虞夫的「恢復政治權利通知書」，其中寫道朱虞夫2011年因顛覆國家政權罪被判有期徒刑7年、附加剝奪政治權利3年、單處剝奪政治權利1年，算至本月3日執行期已滿，因此依法恢復政治權利。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">不過中國本身在政治方面的高壓環境，恢復政治權利可說是毫無意義</span>，不少網友在下紛紛留言表示「<span class=\"red\">國人政治權力本來為零，當你被政府懲治後就降為負數了，可以隨便處置和欺負你。恢復政治權利就是恢復到零狀態。</span>」、「<span class=\"red\">沒有的東西，剝奪和恢復都毫無意義</span>」、「<span class=\"red\">這一張廢紙有何作用？</span>」、「土共政權的極品幽默」、「彷彿是在向太監實施性制裁後宣布恢復其行房權利」、「我們有政治權利嗎？」、「<span class=\"red\">這是我看到的本年度最大的冷笑話。沒有其它可比的</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/liu_xiaoyuan/status/1367394154221764609?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fliu_xiaoyuan%2Fstatus%2F1367394154221764609%3Fs%3D20&d=eRHmMhW6fCYgFX7Mu85bUvFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=f9f3fe63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fliu_xiaoyuan%2Fstatus%2F1367394154221764609%3Fs%3D20&h=e3f83b3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/liu_xiaoyuan/status/1367394154221764609?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3456985\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3456985&d=eRHmMhW6fCYgFX7Mu85bUvFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=db2f19f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3456985&h=bf22dedb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3456985</a>"},{"pid":"d65c37becc4656371e0225160c66608fdb7d6406","tid":2433510,"uid":337052,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T03:03:42.000Z","msg":"沒有的東西，剝奪和恢復都毫無意義"},{"pid":"a6adff2a4e2c42111952a4686c70169d454f1453","tid":2433510,"uid":47021,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T03:05:08.000Z","msg":"香港咪一鳩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f05fa45704d31968689e460b37c60d3fd313acf","tid":2433510,"uid":155095,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T03:05:57.000Z","msg":"0 x 1億都係 0 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb9acd7c5b07e9cc34981462eda3beb0382f326c","tid":2433510,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8f05fa45704d31968689e460b37c60d3fd313acf","tid":2433510,"uid":155095,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T03:05:57.000Z","msg":"0 x 1億都係 0 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T03:07:41.000Z","msg":"0 x 13億都係 0<br />\n9千萬是0.1"},{"pid":"ae106fd4dd28199dcab0431061c6321f10646efa","tid":2433510,"uid":13503,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T03:09:19.000Z","msg":"香港剝奪政治權利係永久<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d5a1f4c7098a7c46ab3a5eb9f53f76cb91a05b","tid":2433510,"uid":363330,"like":4,"dislike":0